title: Spain suspends symbolic vote on Catalan independence
description:
Spain's constitutional court has suspended a symbolic referendum planned by the Catalan regional government for Sunday.

A full independence referendum planned for November 9 was suspended in September so the “consultation of citizens” was proposed instead.
